This is a weapons list that will eventually be integrated with the armour list, potions list and miscellaneous list.

When complete it will form the almighty ITEMS LIST.

There are 10 classes of weapon/armour, the tier also dictates their material. This is important in armour.
1. awful (1-3)
2. terrible (4-6)
3. bad (7-9)
4. mediocre(10-11)
5. average (12-13)
6. good (14-15)
7. great (16-17)
8. rare (18)
9. unique (19)
10.set items (20)

Will edit in materials at a later date.
